      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON LIZZIE (4) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing sixth (24.37) at this track in a Grade 2/3/4. Has good speed and can quickly clear the tricky draw. Looks suited here and big improvement expected. MAGIC POPPY (1) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Other winner three back (23.63) at this track over 400m. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Can hit the frame this time. COMPTON BOWIE (7) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 3 lengths into second (23.33) at this track in a Other over 400m. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to be in the finish again. ASTON RAMONA (2) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
